article.headline: Jonah Pierce's double-double helps Presbyterian slip past Stephen F. Austin 58-55 in OT
article.description: — Jonah Pierce finished with 15 points and 11 rebounds to help Presbyterian slip past Stephen F. Austin 58-55 in overtime on Thursday night at the Axe 'Em Classic.

article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas -- — Jonah Pierce finished with 15 points and 11 rebounds to help Presbyterian slip past Stephen F. Austin 58-55 in overtime on Thursday night at the Axe 'Em Classic. Carl Parrish scored 11 points and grabbed six rebounds. for the Blue Hose (3-3). Kory Mincy contributed 11 points and three steals. The Lumberjacks (2-3) were led by Matt Hayman, who recorded 12 points and two steals. Juhlawnei Stone added nine points, 13 rebounds and two steals. Keith Lamar finished with nine points. Hayman hit a jumper for Stephen F. Austin with 25 seconds left to force overtime tied at 52. Presbyterian used four free throws to outscore the Lumberjacks 6-3 in OT. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
